BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:7slS7JpzIYD8uSeuryZ6w
SUMMARY:Improv Happy Hour
DTSTAMP:20260413T004631Z
DTSTART:20260418T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for Improv Happy Hour\\\, where comedy is unscripted\\\
	, unpredictable\\\, and unbelievably fun! From movie mashups to literary s
	poofs and bold\\\, experimental comedy\\\, our quick-thinking performers t
	urn your suggestions into hilarious scenes on the spot. \\n\\n\\nThis fami
	ly-friendly show at the iconic Gum Wall in Pike Place Market guarantees a 
	night of laughter\\\, surprises\\\, and improv magic you won’t forget. Bri
	ng your wildest ideas\\\, your loudest laughs\\\, and get ready for a one-
	of-a-kind comedy experience—because at Improv Happy Hour\\\, anything can 
