	rves the right to change delivery methods. Unless otherwise noted\, each p
	erson must have a ticket regardless of age. No babies in arms. There is no
	 elevator. Stairs and ramps only to the balcony level.\nMetal detectors & 
	bag search at door. Arrive early. No weapons. www.stgpresents.org/about/sa
	fety When purchasing ADA accessible seating\, please feel free to contact 
	us by email if assistance is needed with accommodations or companion seati
	ng\; you may reach us at accessibility@stgpresents.org. Each accessible se
	at houses an armless freestanding chair for patrons with mobility impairme
	nts and their companions. Please note that our historic theatre has no ele
	vator to the balcony levels.\n\nhttps://www.ticketmaster.com/stewart-copel
	and-have-i-said-too-seattle-washington-06-28-2026/event/0F0064499938BF30\n
